WEBVTT

00:04:27.708 --> 00:04:30.059
and I coughed and my eyes teared.

00:04:30.083 --> 00:04:33.518
I was too overwhelmed
by my own physical discomfort,

00:04:33.542 --> 00:04:35.268
I didn't even look around at first,

00:04:35.292 --> 00:04:36.559
but when I did,

00:04:36.583 --> 00:04:39.643
what I saw brought me to tears.

00:04:39.667 --> 00:04:43.143
Tens of thousands of newly hatched chicks

00:04:43.167 --> 00:04:46.226
in this darkened warehouse

00:04:46.250 --> 00:04:49.000
with nowhere to go and nothing to do.

00:04:49.917 --> 00:04:53.476
Over the next few months,
I returned many times,

00:04:53.500 --> 00:04:55.226
with filmmaker Raegan Hodge,

00:04:55.250 --> 00:04:57.809
to record, to understand,

00:04:57.833 --> 00:04:59.559
to build trust with Craig.

00:04:59.583 --> 00:05:01.351
And I walked his houses with him